And I'll be driving down the road—I kid you not, it's something we talk about all the time—and I'll be praying in the Holy Spirit.

00:28:35.480 --> 00:28:42.968
He says, "You see that land right there? It just came up for sale."And in the natural, I know I can't buy it.

00:28:42.969 --> 00:28:49.399
I don't have it. But He's talking to me about things, stretching me, making me believe for more.

00:28:49.400 --> 00:28:53.199
And in the natural, the money is not there to buy it, but He talks to me about it.

00:28:53.200 --> 00:29:04.759
He says, "Brandon, that piece of land right there in the next couple of years is going to be worth tens of millions of dollars."I said, "Wow, that's awesome.

00:29:04.760 --> 00:29:16.398
Praise God. It's worth a million dollars right now."So I look it up and sure enough, a couple of years later, just like He said, a developer bought it.

00:29:16.399 --> 00:29:24.743
He put houses on it. It's worth tens of millions just like the Lord said. And I look at those things and I grow.

00:29:24.744 --> 00:29:34.702
It helps me to grow because I realize it helps get that trust level up, because one day He's going to talk and I'm going to have the money and I'm going to buy that land.

00:29:34.703 --> 00:29:40.799
I'm going to do what He said, and you can take it to the bank. God will bless your hands.

00:29:40.800 --> 00:29:49.663
Why? Because I practice His presence. I don't look to Him as a genie in the bottle.

00:29:49.664 --> 00:29:55.869
"Oh God, Holy Ghost, you're like my genie in a little bottle right here. My oil. Tell me what it is.

00:29:55.870 --> 00:30:01.349
Let me have the lottery numbers, lucky snake eyes 77 or whatever."And you got it.

00:30:01.350 --> 00:30:07.087
"And Lord, we're going to make it."No, it's flaky. I look at it. I sow the seed.

00:30:07.088 --> 00:30:15.839
I say, "Father, I spend time with you."And in the least expected times and in unlikely ways, He talks.

00:30:15.840 --> 00:30:25.384
I'll be outside in the yard pulling weeds—and I don't have weeds right now because it's winter, but I'd still go outside and even move a rock around, just sitting out there.

00:30:25.385 --> 00:30:35.679
That's what I did today. I sit out there and I listen because He'll talk whenever your mind is off of your problems.

00:30:35.680 --> 00:30:42.086
Think about how you can pray for somebody else today. Think about how you can maybe pray for your loved ones.

00:30:42.087 --> 00:30:44.833
Like I was praying for my mom and my dad; they're going through hard times.

00:30:44.834 --> 00:30:55.599
You listen to people and you take your eyes off of yourself for a minute and pray for somebody else in their need, and God will speak to you and He'll correct you a lot of the time.

00:30:55.600 --> 00:31:00.039
He'll correct me: "You shouldn't have said that. None of your business.

00:31:00.040 --> 00:31:03.799
You don't need to say that."And I wasn't even looking for what He said.

00:31:03.800 --> 00:31:09.359
But He'll talk in the most unlikely way. You'll be like, "Well, look at that.

00:31:09.360 --> 00:31:16.417
I wasn't even asking for that. But thank you."And I don't just cast it aside. I listen to it and I take note of it.

00:31:16.418 --> 00:31:24.119
I get my phone out and I use the voice recorder because I look at everything He says as precious.

00:31:24.120 --> 00:31:29.900
No matter if I was looking for the answer or not, I take those times to go, "Thank you, sir.

00:31:29.901 --> 00:31:34.316
Thank you, Father. Thank you for taking the time to correct me.

00:31:34.317 --> 00:31:45.799
For you correct those that you love."And Father, you'll teach me how to make the bigger money when I can handle it.

00:31:45.800 --> 00:31:59.919
If I'm not able to handle it and it would destroy me and cost me my marriage or cost me my children, then Father, I thank you that you build the character in me.

00:31:59.920 --> 00:32:12.351
But if I don't have the character to handle it, then Father, I thank you, Lord, that you create in me a clean heart, that I'm able to do what I need to do, and thank you, Lord, that I'm a good steward of what you've given me.

00:32:12.352 --> 00:32:24.959
And you can stretch this dollar until it looks like a rubber band, or the quarter, or whatever you've got.

00:32:24.960 --> 00:32:38.279
But I know that if I can sow my offering into good ground, into your church where you're going—and if your church doesn't have good ground, why are you going there?

00:32:38.280 --> 00:32:46.359
I always check it. Check the ground. Check the pastors. Check it first. Tithe and then sow.

00:32:46.360 --> 00:32:54.359
But don't dump your load of seed into something until you at least check the ground to see where you're sowing into.

00:32:54.360 --> 00:33:02.556
And if you start seeing a turnaround and you start seeing increase, then you give a little bit more and you sow a little bit more.

00:33:02.557 --> 00:33:08.319
But then if you see a cankerworm on it, first check your heart.

00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:12.999
Check your marriage. Make sure there's no strife, because faith works by love.

00:33:13.000 --> 00:33:18.719
Keep the main thing the main thing. Keep the relationship vertical.

00:33:18.720 --> 00:33:23.839
If you go horizontal and look at all this other stuff, it's not always the church's fault.

00:33:23.840 --> 00:33:30.857
You've got to make sure that you're in the right place at the right time doing exactly what He asked you to do and sowing where He tells you to sow, being obedient.

00:33:30.858 --> 00:33:44.382
For instance, I was going to sow my seed for my sacrificial gift this year, and I was going to give it back at Christmas time to the minister, and the Lord said, "No."I said, "Why?

00:33:44.383 --> 00:33:53.814
You don't want me to give it all? I'll give it somewhere else because, Lord, I want to bless your ministry. Let me do this.

00:33:53.815 --> 00:34:04.037
You don't want me to do that?"He said, "Not yet."I said, "But I'd like to get it in there and celebrate at Christmas."Just celebrating You because I'm giving it to You.

00:34:04.038 --> 00:34:09.519
I don't give it to the minister; I give it to Jesus because it's His.

00:34:09.520 --> 00:34:20.994
I don't give it for kudos from the person; I give it to Jesus so He goes, "Well done, Brandon."I don't give it so they'll look and say, "Well, thank you for that extra money, sir.

00:34:20.995 --> 00:34:28.974
I appreciate that. Oh, good job, Brandon."I give it so Jesus looks at me and says it was the heart.

00:34:28.975 --> 00:34:37.237
Even if they don't even acknowledge you, I gave it to Him. It was His Christmas; it's His birthday.

00:34:37.238 --> 00:34:42.319
I sow into the birthday. Let me bless you with a birthday present.

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:46.872
Why? The harvest of souls—that's all He cares about. He's the Lord of the harvest.

00:34:46.873 --> 00:34:55.719
So he said to me, "No, don't give it."And I thought, "Oh no, there must be something wrong.

00:34:55.720 --> 00:35:05.679
Am I in control or You? When do you want me to give it?""I want you to do it on the 27th.""On the 27th?

00:35:05.680 --> 00:35:18.127
Okay."So I told Diana, "We're holding off on that. We're not going to give it at all."She goes, "I don't care, honey.

00:35:18.128 --> 00:35:23.687
We've already talked about that. We're going to sow. We're believing God for 2026. Let's go and get it in the ground.

00:35:23.688 --> 00:35:33.959
The faster it's in the ground, the faster the harvest is."I said, "No, the Lord said wait until the 27th."She goes, "Well, I know you hear the Lord."That's interesting.

00:35:33.960 --> 00:35:46.716
So I waited until I could do it today. And I was so excited about it because I told the Lord, "I'm giving it for my 2026 increase. I'm believing for my 2026 increase.

00:35:46.717 --> 00:35:59.616
I'm believing for our ministry to not have any lack, not anything, and that whatever you tell us to do to grow our ministry in 2026, we're going to have more than enough."So I sow it.

00:35:59.617 --> 00:36:04.294
I went today and I got to put it in there. And I felt the anointing all over it.

00:36:04.295 --> 00:36:11.914
And I pray over it just like we always do. Anoint it with oil, pray over it, take communion, release it by faith.

00:36:11.915 --> 00:36:22.770
We take it as a family, all laying hands on it, praying over the envelope as we put it in the mailbox to go and deliver it because I want it.

00:36:22.771 --> 00:36:32.439
David didn't give anything that didn't cost him something. Everything David gave, it cost him something.

00:36:32.440 --> 00:36:36.314
He even talked about it because they were going to give the sacrifice and he said, "No, no, no.

00:36:36.315 --> 00:36:46.999
It has to cost me something. I'm only going to give something that cost me something."So it makes your flesh squirm.

00:36:47.000 --> 00:36:51.599
When it makes your flesh squirm, it's uncomfortable. And that's what we do.

00:36:51.600 --> 00:37:07.596
And we do it every year. Some years I go, "Oh God, I thank you for this."God loves a cheerful giver. So you help out the people that God tells you to.

00:37:07.597 --> 00:37:16.036
That's why I always say it's easy for me to come at you and say all this because we never ask for anything.

00:37:16.037 --> 00:37:24.651
I'm telling you this out of instruction so you can learn. And you say, "Brandon, it's about your ministry."No.

00:37:24.652 --> 00:37:35.879
I'm not teaching you this to sow to me; I'm teaching this so that you'll learn how to grow in your ministry and what God's called you to do.

00:37:35.880 --> 00:37:43.709
Do you understand? I hate manipulation, especially in churches and big ministries.

00:37:43.710 --> 00:37:51.022
There is a lot of manipulation, especially in the Word of Faith circles.

00:37:51.023 --> 00:37:57.799
I look at it and say you can keep it and use it for whatever the Lord tells you to do.

00:37:57.800 --> 00:38:00.913
I don't think a preacher should ever be manipulating people.

00:38:00.914 --> 00:38:10.743
It's wrong, especially using the platform. Follow the Holy Ghost and do what He tells you to do.

00:38:10.744 --> 00:38:21.559
Mary said, "Whatever He tells you to do, do it."Obey. Fill the water pots with water, and He turned the water into wine.

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:32.679
Whatever He tells you to do, do it. Don't listen to the man of God tugging at your heart with emotional violins.

00:38:32.680 --> 00:38:41.399
"Won't you help me?"No, keep your money. Follow the voice of God for your life.

00:38:41.400 --> 00:38:46.208
I do not like spiritual manipulation. I've seen it done; I worked for some big ministries.

00:38:46.209 --> 00:38:55.079
Don't do this. Don't give out of emotion ever. Give when the Holy Spirit tugs at you.

00:38:55.080 --> 00:39:02.524
Be spirit-led in your giving. Listen to the voice of the Spirit of the Lord concerning this.

00:39:02.525 --> 00:39:18.679
There are too many high notes on the organ and you say, "I feel the Holy Ghost."No, you didn't feel anything.

00:39:18.680 --> 00:39:28.020
This isn't the Holy Ghost; it's flesh, and you're being flaky. I'm not going to be giving out of flakiness.

00:39:28.021 --> 00:39:32.579
I don't care how much you think you need for your orphanage or your project.

00:39:32.580 --> 00:39:46.366
You want to play a high note on a key on your organ to make me feel like I'm feeling the Holy Ghost, and you play the tambourine.

00:39:46.367 --> 00:39:56.119
Sit down. It's flaky. You're all excited and people are falling out.

00:39:56.120 --> 00:40:03.715
It's flakiness, especially in the charismatic circle. Stop it.

00:40:03.716 --> 00:40:20.319
I'm telling you all, when you're led by the Spirit of God and you listen to Him when He tells you to give, and you're not emotionally being fed some baloney, you're going to reap, and God will bless you.

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:26.071
Listen again and check it. Ask your wife or your husband if they feel this way.

00:40:26.072 --> 00:40:28.909
You may not have a husband or wife, but follow the Holy Ghost.

00:40:28.910 --> 00:40:36.248
He'll be your guide. Listen to Him and be led by the Spirit of God.

00:40:36.249 --> 00:40:47.924
I'm so tired of charismatic flakiness. I've seen it all. People giving their last everything.

00:40:47.925 --> 00:40:58.478
My mom and dad were all hyped up in a service one time and gave our only car away because they needed the building fund paid off.

00:40:58.479 --> 00:41:08.876
It was our only car, brand new; my uncle bought it for my dad. We were excited to have it because it was a little Cutlass.

00:41:08.877 --> 00:41:13.161
My dad gave it away because there was a high note on the keyboard, and we suffered.

00:41:13.162 --> 00:41:24.978
We were freezing in the back of a truck all winter long because we didn't have a car to get to church or school.

00:41:24.979 --> 00:41:30.939
My dad got a camper from my grandparents, and it was freezing in the negatives.

00:41:30.940 --> 00:41:40.199
I sat back there with the exhaust fumes, mad at the church because they took my car since Dad got hyped up about someone giving.

00:41:40.200 --> 00:41:53.373
I've seen it. I've lived it, and it's flaky. Don't give out of emotion; give by the Spirit of God leading you.

00:41:53.374 --> 00:42:00.279
People want to know my opinion about it, and I tell you, I've seen it all.

00:42:00.280 --> 00:42:04.629
Some of the biggest people in the biggest ministries have the biggest planes and biggest stuff.

00:42:04.630 --> 00:42:16.239
I don't care if they have it; I want them to be blessed. But never work on an old lady's emotions to get it.

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:27.541
Let it be spirit-led and God will bless your hands. That's my message. There's a mic drop.

00:42:27.543 --> 00:42:44.599
If you listen to what I'm trying to tell you, you'll walk in a greater side of blessing and you'll have more peace instead of being ticked off at the church because people are getting mad about prosperity.

00:42:44.600 --> 00:42:53.400
Just stay in the right lane. Did that help at all? Hopefully.

00:42:53.401 --> 00:43:02.556
I talked too long, but it is what it is. Do you want to pray now?

00:43:02.557 --> 00:43:06.699
I didn't have anything prepared, but the Lord gave you that.

00:43:06.700 --> 00:43:12.926
That came right out of the Holy Ghost. I can feel the presence of the Lord on it.

00:43:12.927 --> 00:43:26.959
He helped me. I just love Him; He's my friend. There is too much flakiness in the church.

00:43:26.960 --> 00:43:36.277
You've seen it. I know there's a lot of corruption going on in there, too.

00:43:36.278 --> 00:43:42.649
I could call them all out, but God would probably get mad at me, and I'd never be on this platform again.

00:43:42.650 --> 00:43:54.579
You'd look at me and go, "Brandon, what did you just say?"because there's a lot of sin in there.

00:43:54.580 --> 00:44:07.799
Seriously bad stuff. But they are held accountable for it on the other side. You think you got away with it, but you didn't.

00:44:07.800 --> 00:44:14.959
You're going to be held accountable for everything you thought you did in private.

00:44:14.960 --> 00:44:22.639
You're going to stand before the Lord one day and give an account for how you handled things.

00:44:22.640 --> 00:44:38.016
To whom much is given, much is required. I'm more scared for you than anything. Some of you are in trouble.

00:44:38.017 --> 00:44:48.657
If people really saw the stink behind the stage, they'd say, "Oh my God."Seriously, that's why Brandon just stays to himself.

00:44:48.658 --> 00:44:58.291
I don't go into all the big preacher circles. I go where the Holy Spirit leads me.

00:44:58.292 --> 00:45:05.116
He says, "Go here, don't go there. Don't go to that platform.

00:45:05.117 --> 00:45:20.435
Follow my voice, son."I asked, "What about this one?"He said, "That's where prophets go to die."No joke.

00:45:20.436 --> 00:45:29.268
He said that's where prophetic voices go to die. When He said that, I got chills. I was driving down the road.

00:45:29.269 --> 00:45:49.999
I told Diana, "This is what He just said."God said, "I'm cleaning house in 2026."First Corinthians 5:5 is going to become manifest in a great capacity for a lot of people.

00:45:50.000 --> 00:46:06.959
It's for those who touch the gold, the glory, and the girls. Judgment begins in my house first. Great TV stations will fall, and they will be no more soon.

00:46:06.960 --> 00:46:12.959
You're going to see ministers that you thought would be on platforms for the rest of their lives who will be no more.

00:46:12.960 --> 00:46:21.103
They'll be like Ananias and Sapphira. They're gone. You're going to go, "What happened there?"No explanation.

00:46:21.104 --> 00:46:33.754
They just went. Not all of them are bad; some are just getting old and need to go home. But some will.

00:46:33.755 --> 00:46:43.983
Over the next three years, you're going to see a lot of new faces coming up—the new Davids, the new Esthers—and you're going to see platforms explode seemingly out of nowhere.

00:46:43.984 --> 00:46:57.651
You're going to go, "Where in the world did they come from?"It's just the hand of the Lord using them because they said, "Here am I, Lord, send me."And you're going to see a lot of the people that were somebodies and such-and-such be nothing.

00:46:57.652 --> 00:47:08.679
It will be just like Saul walking through when the anointing was stripped away from him.

00:47:08.680 --> 00:47:20.999
So, he rises up a new David to take the helm. Will you be my new David? He says, "Will you be my new person?

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:33.439
Here am I, Lord, send me."But if I can't handle it, and I don't want to ever cause pain to any of your people, I don't want to be what I have seen.

00:47:33.440 --> 00:47:41.519
If I don't have the character to handle the anointing, if I don't have the character to handle the platform, don't give it to me.

00:47:41.520 --> 00:47:48.639
If I'm going to hurt thousands and thousands of people in the future and I don't see it, please.

00:47:48.640 --> 00:47:59.119
Because it's like what I heard Joyce say: the bigger the platform, the bigger the level of how many people you can hurt.

00:47:59.120 --> 00:48:10.679
And I don't want to hurt people. And that's why I say, "Lord, create in me a clean heart."Help me stay right with you.

00:48:10.680 --> 00:48:20.599
Because it's staying on that vine, staying on that life source, that's going to get you there.

00:48:20.600 --> 00:48:27.377
It's whenever you separate yourself from the life source that the branch eventually dies.

00:48:27.378 --> 00:48:37.920
The branch doesn't die overnight. Just like it is if you prune a tree, it dies over time.

